{"id":84252,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/07/印度-orkut-访客人数即将被-facebook-超越-2/","date":"2010-07-12T03:01:34Z","modified":"2010-07-12T03:01:34Z","title":"印度 Orkut 访客人数即将被 Facebook 超越","content":"<p><img title=\"orkutfbindia\" src=\"http://www.google.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/orkutfbindia.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"599\" height=\"364\" /></p>\n<p>每次一说Google不懂社交，就会有人跳出来说<a href=\"http://www.google.org.cn/posts/sns-worldmap.html\">人家Orkut在巴西和印度是霸主呢</a>。好吧，这个印度的社交霸主之位马上也要保不住了。根据comScore的统计，Facebook在5月吸引了1800万印度独立访客，而Orkut则是1970万。对比去年，Facebook在印度的访客增长了177%，而Orkut同期只涨了35%。估计等到comScore六月的统计结果出来，Facebook就可以在印度超越Orkut了。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://trends.google.com/websites?q=orkut.com,+facebook.com&amp;geo=IN&amp;date=all&amp;sort=0\">根据Google Trends的分析结果</a>，实际上Orkut在上个月就已经被Facebook超越了：</p>\n<p><img title=\"screen-capture\" src=\"http://www.google.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/screen-capture4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"592\" height=\"228\" /></p>\n<p>Facebook正在印度获得越来越多的资源，包括最近又在当地招了500名员工。</p>\n<p>那么Google社会化的救命草现在就只剩巴西了，Orkut每个月有2900万访客，而Facebook只有800万，Google还能吃一阵老本。<a href=\"http://trends.google.com/websites?q=orkut.com%2C+facebook.com&amp;geo=BR&amp;date=all&amp;sort=0\">Google Trends的结果也能说明</a>Orkut还能在巴西撑得住局面：</p>\n<p><img title=\"screen-capture-1\" src=\"http://www.google.org.cn/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/screen-capture-12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"592\" height=\"226\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.google.org.cn/posts/google-me-coming-soon.html\">最近盛传的Google Me社会化服务</a>能挽救Google在社会化上的溃败吗？</p>\n<p>Via <a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/2010/07/07/orkut-facebook-india/\">TechCrunch</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/1105192/tongji.php\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/389988272/techpost/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://www.google.org.cn/posts/india-orkut-fall-to-facebook-soon.html\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\" height=\"0\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/l/feedsky/techpost/389988272/art01.html\"><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/r/i/feedsky/techpost/389988272/art01.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a title=\"印度 Orkut 访客人数即将被 Facebook 超越\" href=\"http://www.google.org.cn/posts/india-orkut-fall-to-facebook-soon.html\" target=\"_blank\">印度 Orkut 访客人数即将被 Facebook 超越</a></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[20534],"tags":[5644,5908,12864,8641,12011]}